{"_path":"/blog/about-note","_dir":"blog","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"关于记笔记","description":"当你闭上眼睛，回想自己掌握的知识时，你会发现自己掌握的东西少得可怜：","date":"2022-10-17","categories":["Computer technology"],"tags":["Chinese & 中文"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当你闭上眼睛，回想自己掌握的知识时，你会发现自己掌握的东西少得可怜："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2022/12/13/36aeabe8e7563462ac2e2d2c70dbec54.png","style":"zoom:50%;"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我总是怕脑子把学过的东西忘了，相信 “ 好记性不如烂笔头 ” ，把笔记写的很详细（写笔记是相当于要向一个刚入门的小白讲清楚所有知识，也就是做通俗易懂、面面俱到的笔记，以便很多年后我忘掉这些知识以后可以通过笔记快速复习回忆），结果深陷记笔记泥潭进度严重滞后。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其实脑子根本没有那么容易忘记，因为每天都和那些东西打交道。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"现在想学编程，完全可以从网上获取成为一个合格计算机工程师所需的全部资料。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"然而面对 “ 堆积如山 ” 的资料，我意识到想把这么多资料整理到自己的 markdown 笔记里、总结完是不可能的，能认真看完就不错了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"只能把它们归类，然后按原有的形态存着。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以做代学，实战上手边做边学（直接开始研究 / 做中等难度的东西，再降维打击简单的内容，最后打牢基础攻关难的）；不必整合各种学习资料、做详细笔记，看视频和看书脑子理解了，看懂就行。笔记只记录精华思想、感悟即可。学完后有时间再快速归档整理一下笔记，顺便反思研究。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以快速突进掌握实践技术为主，笔记后续跟进迅速完善覆盖。如果是从基础开始学一点做一点笔记、笔记做的特别详细，虽然笔记做的很好，但是可能会严重拖慢进度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"不要什么都记"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不要什么都记"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不要做基础文档笔记：直接复制现有文档就行了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基础知识网上都有，不用记，看已有的文档书籍即可，由 PDF 文件、复制下来的 markdown 文件、HTML 文件 组成。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在学习过基础之后，记录一下 遇到的问题、解决方法、思路、总结 这些中高级笔记。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"技术永远在更新，你的精力有限，不可能把所有东西都做一遍笔记，然后一直维护这些笔记确保它们不过时。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2022/12/13/2048dc5f6e3172152d62a7e63530e2a5.png","style":"zoom:30%;"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"研究计算机基础"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"研究计算机基础"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"学的基础知识底层知识越多越牢，先补一些计算机基础，学新知识也越快。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"计算机知识体系像一棵树🌲，越底层的东西越难。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你从树叶开始入门，如果你只会一根树枝的知识，那你只能轻松精通这一根树枝上所有树叶的知识。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"（树干 = 底层知识：计算机基础；树枝 = 中层知识：框架原理；树叶 = 简单的应用层知识：框架使用）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果你学习了 2 种树枝的知识你就可以快速掌握这 2 个树枝上新长出来的树叶知识，但是要学习其他树枝那就得多花点精力学习了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果你花时间研究明白了树干的知识，那对你来说，学习树枝和树叶就简单了，你可以快速学习几乎任何一个方向，比如前端、后端等等，因为你已经有树干了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"总之，你要成为高级工程师的树干就那么粗，早晚都得学，而且如果掌握了树干，上面长出新树叶就能快速学习了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另一种极端情况：如果只会树叶，不会树枝，就只能拼命跟随树叶，长出来多少树叶，就要学多少树叶。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"技术发展与职业规划"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"技术发展与职业规划"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"技术的发展是很快，新技术层出不穷，迭代非常快。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"阮一峰老师的博客里提出过这个问题。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大致意思是说："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"学习技术的可能过不了 7、8 年就淘汰了。就像在 2007 年刚学习了诺基亚的塞班系统开发，苹果 、安卓又开始偷偷萌芽了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2020 年的时候在武汉大学校园里见过一次无人车，“ 别人家的学校🥹 ” ，当时有很多同学拍照，感觉这黑科技太酷了。但是无人车差不多也只是在 2016、2017 年左右开始火的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"刚毕业时学的技术栈不太可能用到退休（50 年），只能在毕业后的 5 ~ 15 年用上，之后就得靠底层的树干技术学习新树叶了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"（50 年，22 岁到 75 岁左右，这里有为什么 75 岁退休：医疗条件好 > 不愿意生孩子 > 人口老龄化 > 财政税收不能负担退休金 > 延迟退休，所以为什么医疗条件这么好 > 因为科技在爆炸式发展，00 后的人活 120 岁左右）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当一种技术被取代时，相关的工作岗位也就消失了。这种事情在技术行业特别多，因为技术的升级换代太快了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"怎么应对技术太快："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"退出技术行业，转行"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"转管理，或者创业开公司"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"拼命学习，靠基础好、深入底层，学习速度会比年轻人快"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在现在，从"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.ruanyifeng.com/survivor/collapse/university.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"网上"}]},{"type":"text","value":"几乎可以获取所有学习资料。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我很讨厌上课，在上课时我很难学到真正有用的知识，也可能是学校教的内容太传统 😴。于是乎，我上课前都会偷偷卸载教室电脑的投屏授课软件，然后学习我想学的东西，这种感觉很好，感觉时间没有浪费。这样我就能利用上课时间去学习需要的东西。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我不依赖上课，只从图书馆借书或者从网上收集资料（电子书、别人的技术文章、网课）。网课的效率非常高，我可以把视频调到 1.5 倍速，或者跳过我已经知道的地方，直接快进到我想听的地方。当然不是所有人都适合我这种方法，只是我自己喜欢这样学罢了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每个人都有适合自己的学习方法。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2022/12/13/f568df9647bb1aa1a5d034aeeb836306.png","style":"zoom:150%;"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大佬们的想法："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2022/12/13/0548402873a966b9ee39b3aa68279daf.png","style":"zoom:25%;"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2022/12/13/a3668673b8d7973048ce59f0ef14ef28.png","style":"zoom:25%;"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不要限制自己。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2022/12/13/15f945a582794e4f1e5bbc92295e4839.png","style":"zoom:25%;"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主动出击。你可以分析一下公司的产品，然后主动写邮件给公司提出改进意见：“ 我觉得这样更好 ... ” 可能就会得到一份工作。或者在面试前分析一下，在面试是聊到可以提一嘴。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最后，附上 Joel Spolsky 的"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://www.joelonsoftware.com/articles/FindingGreatDevelopers.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"博客"}]},{"type":"text","value":" ：如何找到优秀的人才。"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2008/11/finding_great_developers.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中文翻译版"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"不要什么都记","depth":2,"text":"不要什么都记"},{"id":"研究计算机基础","depth":2,"text":"研究计算机基础"},{"id":"技术发展与职业规划","depth":2,"text":"技术发展与职业规划"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:blog:about-note.md","_source":"content","_file":"blog/about-note.md","_stem":"blog/about-note","_extension":"md"}